::Mosquitor/Zardus::

Mosquitor yells when the femms were right above him, dropping down in his large mosquito form. His large legs try to grab the central femm as he tries to stab his mouthpiece into her. (Note: Mosquitor's mouthpiece deploys thorns when it stabs in, so if its in, it don't come out easy).

Hearing Mosquitor attack, Zardus jumps out from behind his plate, firing a missile at one of the femms that Mosquitor didn't get. He didn't care if Mosquitor was hit by friendly fire.
